NAME
	notice

SYNOPSYS
	notice <target>
	notice everything

OPTIONS
	<target> - the target or targets you want to perform the command
		   on. This may be a name or description of a living or
		   item, singular or plural ie. Mercade, the dwarf wizard,
		   dwarves, sword, weapons, etc, are all valid targets.
      everything - a simple way to notice everything in your environment or
		   inventory. It notices beings (people, monsters, animals)
		   as well as items all in one go for just one gold coin
		   per succesful use.

SEE ALSO
	exploration
